    "steam_appid": 3305700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/595d02212a87653734c244db5ea55cda.avif?t=1757701868\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras_big/595d02212a87653734c244db5ea55cda.avif?t=1757701868 width=800 height=165 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The U.D.E. Corporation offers volunteers the chance to <strong>examine</strong> <strong>the ocean depths for a generous reward.</strong> The protagonist is one of them. At first glance, the job seems easy and well-paid, <strong>but is it really?</strong> The corporation is definitely hiding something...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/20a505fac08b585063db6f3b3da67b0e.webp?t=1757701868\" width=800 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/4760a9a6a06471c40224462d77089d3a.poster.avif?t=1757701868\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/4760a9a6a06471c40224462d77089d3a.webm?t=1757701868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/4760a9a6a06471c40224462d77089d3a.mp4?t=1757701868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be lowered to the depth of 13 kilometeres, into a dark, unexplored world. <strong>You and your rusty craft</strong> - a submarine which you are to pilot and maintain throughout the expedition. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/20a505fac08b585063db6f3b3da67b0e.webp?t=1757701868\" width=800 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/5e59f78033c63d6c41e41e1800a6a46a.poster.avif?t=1757701868\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/5e59f78033c63d6c41e41e1800a6a46a.webm?t=1757701868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/5e59f78033c63d6c41e41e1800a6a46a.mp4?t=1757701868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soon, one thing becomes certain — nothing good awaits. The feeling of being watched. Helpless and alone. Forced into puzzles with your own life at stake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/20a505fac08b585063db6f3b3da67b0e.webp?t=1757701868\" width=800 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/384a2359218574793d4e144f68fab414.poster.avif?t=1757701868\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/384a2359218574793d4e144f68fab414.webm?t=1757701868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/384a2359218574793d4e144f68fab414.mp4?t=1757701868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why are we here just to suffer What secrets does The Corporation hold? What's lurking in that dark abyss? Uncover something everyone fears yet few truly know...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305700/extras/20a505fac08b585063db6f3b3da67b0e.webp?t=1757701868\" width=800 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will die. <strong>No matter what, you will die.</strong> But there's one thing you can control — whether you die at the beginning or die at the very end.</p>",
